{
  "texts": [
    "The authors propose a Geometric Proximity Correlator (GPC) and variational sampling to extract and analyze the morphology of the point clouds.",
    "Their classification tests revealed that the combination of this method with the PointNet (Qi et al. 2017a) method outperforms several other methods in accuracy, losing out to only the Point Transformer Network (Zhao et al. 2021).",
    "This approach outperforms competing models in some of the classes while falling back on others.",
    "Yu et al. (2022) generalize the idea of transformers from BERT (Devlin et al. 2019) for point clouds.",
    "The created method, Point-BERT, is pre-trained using an MPM task."
  ]
}